parameters: C'mon, Roz-chan~\! I know you can do it!
I took care of your problem.\! Don't think they'll be an issue anymore.
Excellent!\! You have my gratitude!\! This is cause for celebration!
We fulfilled our end of the bargain.\! Sorry we have no time for such things.\! Please move the
Gahahaha!\! It's ol' Roz-chan!\! I'm happy to see you!
My invite still stands if you ever change your mind!
Rozzy~\! What brings you to my humble abode?
Hahahaha!\! So that's it?\! Your friend wants to look as beautiful as me?
I'll reveal my secret then~\! But on one condition!
What would you like in exchange?
Bring me sweets fit for a queen of my caliber!\! If you truly live in a time different
from mine, you must have prefected the technique of sweets!
Wait a minute...\! YOU have a sweet tooth?
Of course I do~\! I may be a specimen of a stallion, strong, and gorgeous, but I have
soft and feminine side to me you know~
I-I suppose that's true?\! I-I'll go get your sweets then.
Gahahaha!\! How's the hunt for sweets?
Give the acquired sweet to Nefertiti?
Aaaaahn~\! This sweet was just DELECTABLE~\! Thank you, Rozzy~
Would you be able to share the secrets now?
Sure!\! But I need you to gather a few items for me so I can show you.
Get me...\! 3 mint herbs, 2 blood limes, aaaand some centaur milk!
Wait!\! Centaur milk?\! Where am I supposed to get all this stuff?

Sorry, no one is allowed on the second floor.\! Only my lord, her advisors and
Tch.\! Can't believe she offered you to be part of our harem.\! You're more of a side girl type.
(I should clock her in the face but I'll let her be.\! For now.)
You...\! Now all my lord does is talk about you.\! Can you go away?
You know, I'm ok not being the main focus of her attention.\! Her happiness is all I
Our lord is most cunning!\! Wouldn't you agree?
Ah!\! You are a most welcome guest!\! Could I persuade to join my lord's harem?
My lord has an appetite~\! She seems to eat an army's worth of food.
I'm jealous of my lord's two new lovers...\! Maybe I should tone up my body some more!
Don't try anything funny around my lord!
Even though I'm a guard, I've been assigned cleaning duty.\! It's always a nightmare.
My lord, these are the people that demanded an audience with you.
I have eyes, Oli.\! I can see them.
Hey, blondie!\! You're quite the looker.\! What's your name?
That's a cute name~\! Wanna be part of my harem?
Pardon, madam.\! My partner and I are here for pressing matters.\! We're not here
Sigh, I'm not interested in you, big girl.\! My type is small, like her~
Whatever.\! We're here to talk about a boulder blocking the path on the North end of the desert.
We were wondering if you know of a way to move it!
I suppose I do.\! I could move it.
Not so fast, princess.\! For one, Nefertiti doesn't do things for free, and two...\!
Even if I were to move it, some cursed monsters keep putting boulders back there.
So you have attempted to move those before.
I know~\! You could take care of those monsters for me.
Wait a minute nothing.\! You want me to move those rocks and I want those monsters
gone.\! Earn your trust by helping me out.
Tch.\! C'mon, let's get going then, Roz-chan.
Hold on there.\! I have a single stipulation.
You can't help her, big girl.
Eh, I want her to win over my trust.\! Not you.\! I feel you would make it easy.\!
Guess I'll go take care of the problem then.
Fine.\! I'll wait for you here.
Good luck out there.\! Sorry I can't help.
Roz-chan!\! What brings you to my humble abode?\! What happened to your grumpy friend?\!
She had her power stripped and now you're trying to get it back?\! Hmmm...
Please, if you know of a way of getting Hildr back to full strength, tell us!
Personally I don't know anything about mana or whatever.\! I just know how to use it.\! Maybe if you
find elementalists or scholars or whatever, they might be able to help.
That at least points us in a good direction.\! Thanks!
I wish you good luck, and Hildr a speedy recovery.\! Also...\! Don't forget my offer to join
